## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python {{ python_version }}+
- [UV](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) package manager
- [go-task](https://taskfile.dev/) task runner
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) for frontend
- {{ container_runtime }} for containers

### Setup

```bash
# Install dependencies
task backend:dev

# Start development server
uv run uvicorn {{ project_slug }}.main:app --reload

# Or use containers
task docker:up
```

### Development Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `task backend:dev` | Install Python dependencies |
| `task backend:test` | Run test suite via tox |
| `task backend:lint` | Run linters (Ruff) |
| `task backend:format` | Auto-format code |
| `task backend:typecheck` | Run type checker |
| `task frontend:dev` | Start frontend dev server |
| `task frontend:test` | Run frontend tests |
| `task docker:up` | Start all containers |
| `task docker:down` | Stop all containers |

### API Documentation

- Swagger UI: http://localhost:8000/api/docs
- ReDoc: http://localhost:8000/api/redoc

